{"tid":1182410,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"36歲謝婷婷外國秘密產女　晒BB手仔報喜","createTime":"2019-06-02T07:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T08:34:19.000Z","uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4eeb52365ed36b8aff49116961c4d53c75e17433","tid":1182410,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"現年36歲藝人謝婷婷早前一直有傳於外國秘密產子，佢今日突然喺社交網上載一張捉住BB手仔嘅相，留言：「You are my brightest light.（你是我最亮的光）」仲透露係囡囡嚟，依家已經一百日大。唔少圈中人包括好友鄭欣宜、鍾嘉欣、鄭希怡、吳雨霏、丁子高等都留言祝賀。而佢去年5月出席活動時身形依然Fit爆，並指仍然單身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190602/photo/bkn-20190602120613593-0602_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190602150352\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190602%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190602120613593-0602_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190602150352&h=2cdfb4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝婷婷經理人回覆：「今日是BB出世一百日，婷婷好開心，亦多謝大家關心，至於其他就等婷婷返嚟再講喇！」而記者就此事致電謝賢，他承認做公公，並笑得開懷：「總之，開心啦！」他指婷婷身在外國，暫時未見過外孫女，問婷婷是否身在美國？四哥笑說：「係啩，哈哈！」至於問到BB的生父是誰，四哥說：「佢鍾意就得啦，你哋唔好咁八卦。（係中國人定外國人？）唔知喎，點會知，總之佢唔喺香港。」<br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒則透過經理人霍汶希表示沒回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190602/bkn-20190602120613593-0602_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190602%2Fbkn-20190602120613593-0602_00862_001.html&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=ebf3c5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190602/bkn-20190602120613593-0602_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e97498680b6178f63d205af12fcf6978c65b08e0","tid":1182410,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"鷹眼個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f7233254bcbb54d7339c7318a083e4218b313b","tid":1182410,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"俾人搞大個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f9de78975ab518c4ffdcc9d6239495411a7260","tid":1182410,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e97498680b6178f63d205af12fcf6978c65b08e0","tid":1182410,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"鷹眼個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"都唔知係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb9e2700dc734bf0764faef8d799a8522f1b129","tid":1182410,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16f9de78975ab518c4ffdcc9d6239495411a7260","tid":1182410,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e97498680b6178f63d205af12fcf6978c65b08e0","tid":1182410,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"鷹眼個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"都唔知係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/dc/35/69/dc3569f29420bdb0c46a94545864a549.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fdc%2F35%2F69%2Fdc3569f29420bdb0c46a94545864a549.gif&h=48f790fc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}